1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正～～ 言下之意 香港政府默許逃犯喺周圍走 鍾意出國又得唔出國又得 去邊都無所謂 <br />\n去日本又得 去美國又得 只不過今次咁啱個犯想去台灣"},{"pid":"99e7ec44132fefa4deb55c28b3ec2be11af08664","tid":1669671,"uid":14087,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:55:56.000Z","msg":"唉 其他777一野唔理 由得個犯放監就完<br />\n我真係唔明你地圍爐開心做乜<br />\n五大訴求呢？死去既手足，被捕既手足呢？"},{"pid":"a19bdee4ee7088abe0fbe5b704779157c8d9e6b9","tid":1669671,"uid":48579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:56:11.000Z","msg":"初心？而家人地嚟收喎 你號初心去咗邊"},{"pid":"37a7d8c9de480199b7aa019625b667a3832dc479","tid":1669671,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a114a1fe7011598bd5165fd75e53da1974839282","tid":1669671,"uid":87176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正～～ 言下之意 香港政府默許逃犯喺周圍走 鍾意出國又得唔出國又得 去邊都無所謂 <br />\n去日本又得 去美國又得 只不過今次咁啱個犯想去台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"咁香港法律係咁就無辦法，大劉夠可以周圍走。"},{"pid":"2a04919f09a2e42a77ab26ce63f937a7ba9f2c14","tid":1669671,"uid":282851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:58:33.000Z","msg":"陳同佳或成最大贏家<br />\n聽日一search自己原來咁多post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}